<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3933767>
    dc:description "FIGURES 20–25. Afrodontella septemlobata: 20, dorsal chaetotaxy; 21, tibiotarsus and claw III; 22, tibiotarsus and claw II; 23, PAO and ocelli; 24, dens and mucro; 25, antennal chaetotaxy. Scales: 0.1 mm (20), 0.02 mm (21–25)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3933767/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

